block content
  section.position-relative
    img.position-absolute.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover.object-position-bottom(src="images/banner.jpg", alt="")
    .container.position-relative
      .row.h-580px
        .col-md-5.offset-md-1.align-self-center
          .text-dark
            p.mb-0 健身輕時尚
            h1.fs-3.fs-md-1 DOYOGA，做你的瑜珈
            p.fs-5.fs-md-4.mb-1 多給自己一點時間享受靜謐，傾聽內心的聲音。
