      p.fs-5.text-primary DOYOGA 可以帶給你...
    
    ul.row.row-cols-1.row-cols-md-3.gy-1.list-unstyled
      li.col
        a.position-relative.d-flex.align-items-end.h-420px.h-md-252px.h-lg-420px(href="javasctript:;" class="p-1.5")
          img.rounded-3.position-absolute.top-0.start-0.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover(src="images/photo01.jpg", alt="整體健身")
          .position-relative.text-white
            h3.fs-5.fw-normal 整體健身
            p.mb-0 每一個動作，都融入運動解剖學的的觀點強調以身體的中心線為出發點。
      li.col
        a.position-relative.d-flex.align-items-end.h-420px.h-md-252px.h-lg-420px(href="javasctript:;" class="p-1.5")
          img.rounded-3.position-absolute.top-0.start-0.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover(src="images/photo02.jpg", alt="整體健身")
