            h3.fs-5.fw-normal 減壓放鬆
            p.mb-0 調節全身系統、改善血液循環、減壓養心、釋放身心，達到修心養性的目的。
      li.col
        a.position-relative.d-flex.align-items-end.h-420px.h-md-252px.h-lg-420px(href="javasctript:;" class="p-1.5")
          img.rounded-3.position-absolute.top-0.start-0.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover(src="images/photo03.jpg", alt="局部雕塑")
          .position-relative.text-white
            h3.fs-5.fw-normal 局部雕塑
            p.mb-0 幫助強化背部與腹部的核心肌群，增進我們身體穩定度以及保持良好體態。

  section.bg-light(class="py-3 py-md-4")
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-6.d-none.d-lg-block
          .rounded-3.overflow-hidden.position-relative.h-100
            img.w-100.h-100.object-fit-cover.position-absolute(src="images/photo04.jpg", alt="頂尖師資、專業教學")
        .col-md(class="py-0 py-md-2").align-self-center.position-relative
          h2.fs-3.text-secondary.text-center.text-lg-start 頂尖師資、專業教學
          p.fs-5.text-primary(class="col-md-8 offset-md-2 col-lg-12 offset-lg-0") 強力師資，經歷豐富，協會認證。運用引導式教學，針對不同需求的人制定專屬課程。
          div(class="col-md-10 offset-md-2 col-lg-12 offset-lg-0")
            ul.d-grid.gap-1.list-unstyled.m-0.text-dark(class="mt-1.5")
              li.bg-white.rounded-3(class="p-1 px-md-3 py-md-2.5 ms-md--5")
                .d-flex.align-items-center(class="gap-1.25")
                  div.col-2.col-md-auto
                    img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src="images/teacher-1.png", alt="Carol Tang 老師")
                  div
                    h3.fs-5.fw-normal(class="mb-0.5") Carol Tang 老師
                    p(class="mb-0.5") 教學經歷 10 年
                    p(class="mb-0") 瑜珈讓我重新認識自己的身體，也讓我有了不一樣的人生。

              li.bg-white.rounded-3(class="p-1 px-md-2 py-md-1.5")
                .d-flex.align-items-center(class="gap-1.25")
                  div.col-2.col-md-auto
                    img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src="images/teacher-2.png", alt="Carol Tang 老師")
                  div
                    h3.fs-5.fw-normal(class="mb-0.5") Kanae 老師
                    p(class="mb-0") 教學經歷 10 年

              li.bg-white.rounded-3(class="p-1 px-md-2 py-md-1.5")
                .d-flex.align-items-center(class="gap-1.25")
                  div.col-2.col-md-auto
                    img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src="images/teacher-3.png", alt="Carol Tang 老師")
                  div
                    h3.fs-5.fw-normal(class="mb-0.5") Asa Ifrit 老師
                    p(class="mb-0") 教學經歷 10 年

  section.container(class="py-3 py-md-4")
    .row.align-items-center(class="gx-1 gx-md-2")
      .col-12.col-md-6.col-lg-5.order-md-last.my-1
        h2.fs-3.text-secondary 舒適空間、靜心放鬆
        p.fs-5.text-primary 強力師資，經歷豐富，協會認證。運用引導式教學，針對不同需求的人制定專屬課程。
        a.link-secondary(href="javasctript:;")
          .d-flex.align-items-center
            |環境介紹
            span.material-icons-outlined(class="ms-0.5") arrow_right_alt
      
      .col-6.col-md-4
        .ratio.ratio-3x4
          img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo05.jpg")

      .col-6.col-md-2
        .d-grid.gap-2
          .ratio.ratio-3x4
            img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo09.jpg")
          .ratio.ratio-3x4.d-none.d-sm-block
            img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo10.jpg")

  section.bg-light.overflow-hidden
    .container(class="py-3 py-md-4")
      .row.position-relative.align-items-center
        .col-md-6.col-lg-5.offset-lg-1.my-1
          h2.fs-3.text-secondary 精心設計、課程多元
          p.fs-5.text-primary 教師帶領多元課程，釋放壓力，與身心常見的緊繃不適溫柔和解。
          a.link-secondary(href="javasctript:;")
            .d-flex.align-items-center
              |課程介紹
              span.material-icons-outlined(class="ms-0.5") arrow_right_alt
        
        //- 卡位用 Start 用來幫下個區塊的 absolute 的位置卡位
        .col-md-5.invisible.d-none.d-xl-block
          .ratio.ratio-1x1
            img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo06.jpg")
        //- 卡位用 End

        .col-md.offset-xl-6.position-xl-absolute.top-0
          .row.flex-xl-nowrap.overflow-scroll(class="g-1 g-md-1.5")
            .col-6.col-xl-5
              .ratio.ratio-1x1
                img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo06.jpg")
            .col-6.col-xl-5
              .ratio.ratio-1x1
                img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo07.jpg")
            .col-6.col-xl-5
              .ratio.ratio-1x1
                img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo08.jpg")
            .col-6.col-xl-5
              .ratio.ratio-1x1
                img.object-fit-cover.rounded-3(src="images/photo12.jpg")
            .col-xl-4.m-0

  section.container(class="py-3 py-md-4")
    .text-center.mb-2
      h2.fs-3.text-secondary 方案選擇
      p.fs-5.text-primary DOYOGA 可以帶給你...
    ul.row.row-cols-xl-3.row-cols-1.list-unstyled(class="gy-1.5")
      li.col
        .card.rounded-3.border-primary.overflow-hidden
          .row.g-0
            .col-md.col-xl-12
              .ratio.ratio-4x3.h-100
                img.object-fit-cover(src="images/photo12.jpg", alt="首次體驗")
            .col-md.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-between
              .card-body.text-secondary(class="p-1.5")
                .text-center.text-md-start.text-xl-center(class="mb-0.5")
                  h3.fs-5.fw-normal 首次體驗
                  .fs-5.text-primary NT $450 / 次
                p.card-text 分基礎、中級、高級可以選擇。初次至DOYOGA 上課建議選擇此方案。
              div(class="p-1.5")
                a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.w-100.text-white(href="javasctript:;") 選擇課程
      li.col
        .card.rounded-3.border-primary.overflow-hidden
          .row.g-0
            .col-md.col-xl-12
              .ratio.ratio-4x3.h-100
                img.object-fit-cover(src="images/photo14.jpg", alt="短期體驗")
            .col-md.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-between
              .card-body.text-secondary(class="p-1.5")
                .text-center.text-md-start.text-xl-center(class="mb-0.5")
                  h3.fs-5.fw-normal 短期體驗
                  .fs-5.text-primary NT $1800 / 月
                p.card-text 分基礎、中級、高級可以選擇。想試著培養瑜珈習慣者可以選擇此方案。
              div(class="p-1.5")
                a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.w-100.text-white(href="javasctript:;") 選擇課程

      li.col
        .card.rounded-3.border-primary.overflow-hidden
          .row.g-0
            .col-md.col-xl-12
              .ratio.ratio-4x3.h-100
                img.object-fit-cover(src="images/photo11.jpg", alt="長期體驗")
            .col-md.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-between
              .card-body.text-secondary(class="p-1.5")
                .text-center.text-md-start.text-xl-center(class="mb-0.5")
                  h3.fs-5.fw-normal 長期體驗
                  .fs-5.text-primary NT $5600 / 季
                p.card-text 分基礎、中級、高級可以選擇。有長期習慣做瑜伽者建議選擇此方案。
              div(class="p-1.5")
                a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.w-100.text-white(href="javasctript:;") 選擇課程

  - var userData = [{name:'Joanne', content:'服務很好、設備優良！'},{name:'穎旻', content:'上課後身體健康很多'},{name:'子琪', content:'上課很有趣！'},{name:'葉子', content:'老師的教學很專業'},{name:'Ray', content:'很舒壓'},{name:'俊儀', content:'讚的！'}]
  section.bg-light
    .container-xl.px-md-0.px-xl-1(class="py-3 py-md-4")
      .text-center.mb-2
        h2.fs-3.text-secondary 聽聽他們怎麼說
      
      .swiper-container.columnSwiper.px-md-1.px-xl-0
        .swiper-wrapper
          each val, index in userData
            .swiper-slide
              .bg-white.rounded-3(class="p-1 px-md-2 py-md-1.5")
                .d-flex.align-items-center(class="gap-1.25")
                  div.col-2.col-md-auto
                    img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src="images/user-"+ (index+1) +".png", alt=val.name)
                  div
                    h3.fs-6.fw-normal(class="mb-0.5")
                      |#{val.name}
                      span.small(class="ms-0.5") Oct 17 2020
                    .text-primary(class="mb-0.5")
                      span.material-icons-outlined star_purple500
                      span.material-icons-outlined star_purple500
                      span.material-icons-outlined star_purple500
                      span.material-icons-outlined star_purple500
                      span.material-icons-outlined star_purple500
                    p(class="mb-0") #{val.content}
        .d-flex.justify-content-between.d-md-none
          .swiper-button-prev
            span.material-icons-outlined.fs-2 west
          .swiper-button-next
            span.material-icons-outlined.fs-2 east